IN RE: CONFIDENTIAL PARTY NO. 2018-B-0189 Supreme Court of Louisiana. March 9, 2018

ORDER

Considering the Joint Petition for Consent Discipline filed by respondent and the Office of Disciplinary Counsel, IT IS ORDERED that the Joint Petition for Consent Discipline be and hereby is rejected pursuant to Supreme Court Rule XIX, § 20.

IT IS FURTHER ORDERED that this matter be remanded for consideration of the previously filed formal charges.

Johnson, C.J., recused.
